music; across five aprils - blue eyed suicide once again, i haven't updated in a while. i've been kinda busy. wednesday i went to the mall with dave. we were there for a whole 10 minutes, if that. then we drove around while he serenaded me. then we parked in front of some house. about 30 minuets later some car is flashing their high beams..and we are like what the fuck..then the sirens go on. so the cop said someone called the cops on us for being parked outside for two hours and being suspicious. hmm...30 minutes..two hours..close. so dave had to give him his lisence, registration, all that stuff. and the cop came back and says his registration is 5 days expiered. to make a very very long story short..they ended up towing his car, he got a ticket, and we both got a ride in the back of a cop car to my house. thursday i worked, after school. hung out with april and ended up sleeping over. we didnt have school friday so me april carly and paulina hung out. haha. friday, adrian drove me and carly to the mall. i bought clothes and wasted all my money. i also got stuff for my mom for mothers day. saturday, today, i went out to eat with my rents, brother and jackie. we celebrated mothers day and my jackie's birthday. thats all. night <3
